***Basic Setup For the Project***
Have Anaconda Installed on your PC
Create an environment of your desired name:
i.e
>> conda create -n myEnv python = 3.8.5

***Installing Libraris***
-> Python = 3.8.5 used currently

option 1:
Note:First activate you're previouly created environment
>> conda activate myEnv
(myEnv) >> conda install --file requirements.txt

option 2(Manual):
Note:First activate you're previouly created environment
>> conda activate myEnv
(myEnv) >> conda config --add channels conda-forge
(myEnv) >> conda install matplotlib
(myEnv) >> conda install mpi4py
(myEnv) >> conda install pyfmi

***Running Code***
(myEnv) >> cd SimulationCode
(myEnv) >> mpiexec -n 2 python Main.py

